# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:14
translate portuguese lisa0_b7252674:

    # "When I walk into the hallway, I can hear the TV on in the living room, playing the local news."
    "Quando entro no corredor, ouço a televisão ligada na sala, a passar as notícias locais."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:18
translate portuguese lisa0_f4abcc94:

    # "I pop my head in and see Lisa sitting on the couch alone, watching with her fist in her mouth and tears in her eyes."
    "Espreito e vejo a Lisa sentada sozinha no sofá, a ver com a mão na boca e lágrimas nos olhos."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:21
translate portuguese lisa0_29614313:

    # pc "Is everything okay?"
    pc "Está tudo bem?"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:22
translate portuguese lisa0_2e57e50b:

    # "Lisa startles at my voice and turns, motioning me to come sit next to her."
    "A Lisa sobressalta-se com a minha voz e vira-se, fazendo-me sinal para me sentar ao lado dela."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:25
translate portuguese lisa0_57c2c4c0:

    # sp "I don't know. They said that they found a body in the lake. They haven't said anything else about it."
    sp "Não sei. Disseram que encontraram um corpo no lago. Não disseram mais nada sobre isso."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:26
translate portuguese lisa0_bf28e1a1:

    # pc "Oh."
    pc "Oh."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:27
translate portuguese lisa0_e8fad33f:

    # sp "Oh God, I hope it's not your father. I don't know what I'd do."
    sp "Oh Deus, espero que não seja o teu pai. Não sei o que faria."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:29
translate portuguese lisa0_dacdc92d:

    # "She puts her arms around me and leans her head against my shoulder, tears soaking into my t-shirt."
    "Ela abraça-me e encosta a cabeça ao meu ombro, com as lágrimas a molharem a minha t-shirt."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:30
translate portuguese lisa0_c0e958bb:

    # pc "Let's wait and see if they say anything else. It's probably not him."
    pc "Vamos esperar para ver se dizem mais alguma coisa. Provavelmente não é ele."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:31
translate portuguese lisa0_f981c957:

    # sp "They said that they were going to talk about it, but then they started talking about sports."
    sp "Disseram que iam falar sobre isso, mas depois começaram a falar de desporto."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:32
translate portuguese lisa0_46d1c4b7:

    # sp "Who gives a shit about sports?"
    sp "Quem é que se importa com desporto?"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:33
translate portuguese lisa0_c5d4ed79:

    # "I put my arm around her shoulder and hold her there until the newscasters finally start talking about the story that had her so worked up."
    "Passo o braço pelos ombros dela e seguro-a ali até que os apresentadores finalmente comecem a falar da notícia que a deixou tão perturbada."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:34
translate portuguese lisa0_1a0e9286:

    # "News Anchor" "A sad story today coming out of Carpenter's Bluffs."
    "News Anchor" "Uma notícia triste hoje vinda de Carpenter's Bluffs."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:35
translate portuguese lisa0_b07c79d6:

    # "News Anchor" "The body of a seven-year-old girl was pulled out of Lake Daniel today. It's believed that she drowned."
    "News Anchor" "O corpo de uma menina de sete anos foi retirado do Lago Daniel hoje. Acredita-se que ela se tenha afogado."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:37
translate portuguese lisa0_4712dd31:

    # sp "Oh, thank God."
    sp "Oh, graças a Deus."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:38
translate portuguese lisa0_7e1f8bdb:

    # sp "I mean, it's horrible that this girl drowned. I feel so bad for the parents. But I'm so relieved that it wasn't your father."
    sp "Quero dizer, é horrível que esta menina se tenha afogado. Sinto-me tão mal pelos pais. Mas estou tão aliviado por não ter sido o teu pai."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:40
translate portuguese lisa0_832250a2:

    # sp "Does that make me a bad person?"
    sp "Isso faz de mim uma pessoa má?"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:47
translate portuguese lisa0_5b7eede0:

    # sp "I feel horrible. I heard that they had found a body on the radio on the way home from work and all I could think about was them pulling your father's body out of that lake."
    sp "Sinto-me péssima. Ouvi na rádio, a caminho do trabalho, que tinham encontrado um corpo e só conseguia pensar que estavam a retirar o corpo do teu pai daquele lago."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:48
translate portuguese lisa0_4a8505ff:

    # sp "I just want him to come home."
    sp "Só quero que ele volte para casa."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:49
translate portuguese lisa0_d457cf73:

    # pc "I know, me too."
    pc "Eu sei, eu também."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:51
translate portuguese lisa0_e4d28bf7:

    # "The news is talking about sports and she sits, frustrated, sobbing quietly, her shoulders quivering."
    "As notícias estão a falar de desporto e ela fica sentada, frustrada, a soluçar baixinho, com os ombros a tremer."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:52
translate portuguese lisa0_652f2570:

    # "Then the news anchor comes on."
    "Então, o apresentador das notícias entra em cena."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:53
translate portuguese lisa0_1a0e9286_1:

    # "News Anchor" "A sad story today coming out of Carpenter's Bluffs."
    "News Anchor" "Uma história triste hoje vinda de Carpenter's Bluffs."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:54
translate portuguese lisa0_b07c79d6_1:

    # "News Anchor" "The body of a seven-year-old girl was pulled out of Lake Daniel today. It's believed that she drowned."
    "News Anchor" "O corpo de uma menina de sete anos foi retirado do Lago Daniel hoje. Acredita-se que ela se tenha afogado."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:56
translate portuguese lisa0_4712dd31_1:

    # sp "Oh, thank God."
    sp "Oh, graças a Deus."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:57
translate portuguese lisa0_3fec87b7:

    # "After this, she practically collapses, falling onto the couch crying."
    "Depois disto, ela praticamente desaba, caindo no sofá a chorar."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:62
translate portuguese lisa0_388aa2a0:

    # "I go sit on the couch next to her and put my hand on her leg. She startles a bit and looks up at me."
    "Vou sentar-me no sofá ao lado dela e coloco a minha mão na sua perna. Ela sobressalta-se um pouco e olha para mim."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:63
translate portuguese lisa0_fa75bbc3:

    # pc "Are you okay?"
    pc "Estás bem?"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:66
translate portuguese lisa0_979ec6b9:

    # "Then she stands up and wrapped her arms around me, crying into my shoulder."
    "Depois, ela levanta-se e abraça-me, chorando no meu ombro."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:67
translate portuguese lisa0_3a8c04ee:

    # sp "Oh [pcname]. I heard on the radio on the way home that they had found a body in the lake."
    sp "Oh [pcname]. Ouvi na rádio, a caminho de casa, que tinham encontrado um corpo no lago."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:68
translate portuguese lisa0_d8fada48:

    # sp "I thought for sure that it was going to be your father. All I could think about was them pulling him out of that lake."
    sp "Tinha a certeza de que ia ser o teu pai. Só conseguia pensar neles a retirá-lo daquele lago."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:69
translate portuguese lisa0_eb42ef9d:

    # sp "I feel horrible for the family of that little girl, but also so relieved that it wasn't him."
    sp "Sinto-me péssima pela família daquela menina, mas também tão aliviada por não ter sido ele."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:70
translate portuguese lisa0_4a8505ff_1:

    # sp "I just want him to come home."
    sp "Só quero que ele volte para casa."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:71
translate portuguese lisa0_0437bdda:

    # pc "I know. Me too."
    pc "Eu sei. Eu também."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:73
translate portuguese lisa0_3ebc1e66:

    # "I really don't want to deal with this."
    "Não quero mesmo lidar com isto."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:74
translate portuguese lisa0_e7176023:

    # "I sneak past her and head up to my room, feeling a little bad about it."
    "Passo por ela sem fazer barulho e vou para o meu quarto, sentindo-me um pouco mal por causa disso."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:80
translate portuguese lisa0_bdd243f5:

    # sp "Well, crisis averted for now. Back to just worrying about him constantly."
    sp "Bem, crise evitada por agora. De volta a preocupar-me constantemente com ele."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:81
translate portuguese lisa0_960d3968:

    # "She pulls back and wipes her eyes before straightening her back and recomposing herself."
    "Ela afasta-se e limpa os olhos antes de endireitar as costas e recompor-se."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:82
translate portuguese lisa0_3a601a62:

    # sp "I don't feel like cooking tonight. How does Chinese delivery sound?"
    sp "Não me apetece cozinhar esta noite. Que tal pedir comida chinesa?"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:83
translate portuguese lisa0_8a4e8f18:

    # pc "Sounds great to me."
    pc "Parece-me ótimo."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:84
translate portuguese lisa0_17107884:

    # sp "I'll order something for us, and you can tell me all about your day."
    sp "Vou encomendar algo para nós e podes contar-me tudo sobre o teu dia."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:85
translate portuguese lisa0_1f01ca05:

    # "She calls in the order and we sit and chat afterwards while waiting for it to show up."
    "Ela faz a encomenda e sentamo-nos a conversar enquanto esperamos que a comida chegue."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:86
translate portuguese lisa0_fe09c3bf:

    # "I tell her all about school and my new job and everything."
    "Conto-lhe tudo sobre a escola, o meu novo emprego e tudo o resto."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:88
translate portuguese lisa0_b202d8fe:

    # sp "Wow, you got so much done in a single day. That's pretty amazing!"
    sp "Uau, fizeste tanta coisa num único dia. É incrível!"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:89
translate portuguese lisa0_dd988e66:

    # "She tells me about her day. She is the manager for the helpdesk of an insurance company, with a small team of people underneath her."
    "Ela conta-me sobre o seu dia. É gestora do serviço de assistência de uma seguradora, com uma pequena equipa de pessoas a trabalhar para ela."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:90
translate portuguese lisa0_f9e557b5:

    # "It isn't a job that she loves, isn't really what she wants to do with her life, but it paid the bills enough when it had been both her and Dad."
    "Não é um trabalho que ela adore, não é realmente o que quer fazer da vida, mas pagava as contas quando era ela e o pai."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:91
translate portuguese lisa0_4127ee35:

    # "Without his income however, she is worried about how she is going to keep the house, the car, and pay for all the utilities."
    "Sem o rendimento dele, no entanto, está preocupada em como vai manter a casa, o carro e pagar todas as contas."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:92
translate portuguese lisa0_4f98b5f9:

    # pc "Maybe I could help some?"
    pc "Talvez eu possa ajudar um pouco?"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:93
translate portuguese lisa0_6c559b87:

    # sp "Oh no, I couldn't ask you to do that. You are always welcome here. You never have to pay rent. I'm just happy you're here."
    sp "Oh não, não te posso pedir para fazeres isso. És sempre bem-vinda aqui. Nunca tens de pagar renda. Estou apenas feliz por estares aqui."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:94
translate portuguese lisa0_fe4fee11:

    # pc "Well I'm at least going to help out around the house then. What could I do?"
    pc "Bem, então vou pelo menos ajudar nas tarefas da casa. O que posso fazer?"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:96
translate portuguese lisa0_fa250b58:

    # sp "Well the lawn really needs to be mowed. That's all I can think of right now, but if I think of anything else, I'll let you know."
    sp "Bem, o relvado precisa mesmo de ser cortado. É tudo o que me ocorre neste momento, mas se me lembrar de mais alguma coisa, digo-te."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:97
translate portuguese lisa0_930771f0:

    # pc "I'll get everything fixed. Promise."
    pc "Vou tratar de tudo. Prometo."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:98
translate portuguese lisa0_cf109e47:

    # sp "You're the best. Thank you."
    sp "És o melhor. Obrigada."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:100
translate portuguese lisa0_6e7abadd:

    # sp "I can't think of anything right now honey, but thank you."
    sp "Não me ocorre nada neste momento, querida, mas obrigada."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:101
translate portuguese lisa0_2bb585f4:

    # pc "Anything you need, anything at all, just ask me okay? I'm here to help you out."
    pc "Se precisares de alguma coisa, qualquer coisa, basta pedires, está bem? Estou aqui para te ajudar."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:102
translate portuguese lisa0_9ff5fd48:

    # "Lisa smiles, tears in her eyes."
    "A Lisa sorri, com lágrimas nos olhos."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:103
translate portuguese lisa0_b7cc7411:

    # sp "I really couldn't ask for a better person in my life. That goes both ways, okay? If there's anything that I can help you with, you be sure to tell me too."
    sp "Não poderia pedir uma pessoa melhor na minha vida. Isso vale para os dois, está bem? Se houver alguma coisa em que eu te possa ajudar, não te esqueças de me dizer também."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:104
translate portuguese lisa0_8ce61eb8:

    # "I nod."
    "Aceno com a cabeça."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:105
translate portuguese lisa0_5bc44b07:

    # pc "I will."
    pc "Vou dizer."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisa0.rpy:106
translate portuguese lisa0_f1319eeb:

    # "Finally, when the Chinese food is delivered, we eat in front of the television, then say our goodnights and I head up to my bedroom, completely exhausted after what felt like a very long day."
    "Finalmente, quando a comida chinesa é entregue, comemos em frente à televisão, depois damos as boas-noites e eu subo para o meu quarto, completamente exausto depois do que pareceu um dia muito longo."

